Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.56,0:06:33.23,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(600,600)\pos(715,475)\fsp2\blur5}吴越同舟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.80,0:00:06.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没起作用啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.82,0:00:09.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅如此 反而给大家添了很多麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.46,0:00:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小李 你总是很积极啊 心烦了出身汗就能忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.33,0:00:18.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.67,0:00:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这并非汗水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.87,0:00:22.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是不甘的眼泪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.53,0:00:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定下次一定要帮上忙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.37,0:00:27.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此刻正在做万全的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.59,0:00:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:31.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次我也一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:35.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡卡西老师
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.94,0:00:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人他…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.08,0:00:41.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:43.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那孩子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.54,0:00:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕就是那个拥有操纵三尾能力的少年了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.34,0:01:04.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说三尾从湖中消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.68,0:01:06.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但事情并未就此结束
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.21,0:01:08.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待封印班恢复后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.13,0:01:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再度进行结界四方封阵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.92,0:01:15.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 这孩子现在还不能移动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.07,0:01:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等病情好转后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.82,0:01:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要将他转移到更安全的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.09,0:01:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前 我们要搜索鸣人的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.56,0:01:25.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:27.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.29,0:01:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可是鸣人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.45,0:01:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没准现在正在湖里游着泳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.64,0:01:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和 佐井 牙 雏田
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.45,0:01:40.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们五人负责搜索鸣人的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静音 考虑到鸣人也许会受伤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.26,0:01:46.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就与我们同行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.21,0:01:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱 井野 这孩子的治疗就交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.57,0:01:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,余下的各位负责守护工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.64,0:01:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人一定会回来抢这个孩子的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.40,0:01:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不交给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.84,0:02:02.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会出色完成任务 好好保护他的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.30,0:02:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各位 切勿放松 做好自己的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.96,0:02:16.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白眼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:37.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有雏田和牙在 也找不到的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.05,0:02:45.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚进行了三尾封印 我知道你也很累
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.88,0:02:48.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 还是要小心地控制查克拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.22,0:02:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:51.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次会争口气的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要挽救他的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:03:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我只能为祝你们顺利控制查克拉而做半蹲训练了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.36,0:03:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会打扰我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的任务不是护卫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.61,0:03:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.41,0:03:14.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干吗都挤在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.81,0:03:16.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里已经有志乃了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.11,0:03:19.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就去外面巡视吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.58,0:03:23.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你负责屋顶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.33,0:03:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虫子们居然如此虚弱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.87,0:03:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是受三尾查克拉的影响吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.04,0:04:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.62,0:04:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 被三尾那混蛋给吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:10.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 这里是它的体内吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.33,0:04:15.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好硬啊 这胃也太坚硬了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:17.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底都吃了些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.88,0:04:20.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃的是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.14,0:04:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会把幽鬼丸交给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.70,0:04:45.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽鬼丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.33,0:04:47.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.98,0:06:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麟儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.96,0:06:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙 到底想干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然在战斗中突然消失
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.48,0:06:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你的临阵脱逃 我们可被害惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:53.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说嘛 我被红莲紧急召唤不得不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.76,0:07:00.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:08.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干吗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.94,0:07:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真讨厌 这样盯着人家的脸看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.76,0:07:20.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战场上总是瞬息万变的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们别抱怨了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麟儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:33.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们觉不觉得麟儿有些奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.98,0:07:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定胆怯了吧 完全就是临阵逃脱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.58,0:07:41.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说谁临阵逃脱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.61,0:07:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:49.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 又盯着人家看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麟儿也是这样 你们想干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.42,0:08:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有在镜中看过自己的眼神吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.32,0:08:04.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不是看人用的眼神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.97,0:08:10.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个这样下去就要没命了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤势如此严重吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.27,0:08:14.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.46,0:08:15.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 别开玩笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并非玩笑…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.15,0:08:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.20,0:08:20.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查克拉的流动杂乱无章
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 应该说正在走向毁灭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.24,0:08:27.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毁灭…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来你们的对手相当恐怖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.65,0:08:34.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如说 鬼凤你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.19,0:08:39.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概撑不到2小时就会…砰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.94,0:08:45.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的 那我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.32,0:08:48.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住口 我不想听到自己的死法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.77,0:08:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还不想死 兜大人 救救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.61,0:08:57.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是 请您救救我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:09:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.27,0:09:01.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便你们求我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.61,0:09:05.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的医疗忍术也有限
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.31,0:09:09.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.28,0:09:11.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能对同伴做这种事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.95,0:09:15.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请对我们做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.67,0:09:16.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们愿意去做一切
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何痛苦都愿意承受
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:20.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:26.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你们如此诚恳…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是被人利用的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:42.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一直相信的归宿之人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定…一定…会背叛他的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.17,0:09:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.16,0:09:52.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他连容身之处都没了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.33,0:09:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果说思念自己的人之所在就是他的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.59,0:10:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…我…我就要一直做思念之人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:04.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人说的就是这个孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.95,0:10:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人会没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:13.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定在某些地方思念着这个孩子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.31,0:10:17.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.92,0:10:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧 下面我们会保护好你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:23.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没了 没了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.03,0:10:30.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 丢东西了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:32.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.83,0:10:36.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.06,0:10:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没了 没了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.28,0:10:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.82,0:10:52.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是幽鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:56.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.21,0:11:09.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能原谅我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能原谅…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.58,0:11:19.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了人之后 楚楚可怜地说这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.52,0:11:22.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能获得原谅吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:23.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.06,0:11:27.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会有如此美事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.93,0:11:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 快住手 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.32,0:11:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤口…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:57.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你帮我包扎的吗 这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.97,0:11:59.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有何企图
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.90,0:12:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想骗我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.81,0:12:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人在你面前失去了知觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.98,0:12:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为忍者的你 会放过这种机会…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.64,0:12:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对无法战斗的家伙出手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.17,0:12:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种卑鄙的手段我才不屑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:15.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽鬼丸呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.60,0:12:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:20.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时被吞进三尾腹中的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:22.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该只有我们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.81,0:12:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 他还在湖边…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.84,0:12:33.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能被你的同伴带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.93,0:12:37.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可能被我的某位同伴解救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.93,0:12:41.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我可得尽快离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.11,0:12:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后弄清情况
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.00,0:12:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们之间难免一战
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:50.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先打倒你 然后再从这里离开
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.63,0:12:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你休想出去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.17,0:12:55.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非跨过我的尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:12:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊 我也这么觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:02.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:09.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.50,0:13:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的虫子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是小三尾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.26,0:13:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:35.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用我的晶遁…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.09,0:13:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的你怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.42,0:13:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从你目前的伤势来看 根本做不到嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.45,0:13:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.13,0:13:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己能跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.48,0:13:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没了 没了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.28,0:13:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了啊 你找什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.80,0:14:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.53,0:14:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮的水晶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.23,0:14:11.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有一丝伤痕 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.36,0:14:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红莲姐平安无事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.04,0:14:14.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红莲是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是鸣人说的那位牵挂着这个孩子的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.18,0:14:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红莲姐平安无事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.85,0:14:29.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.04,0:14:35.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是被人利用的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.34,0:14:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一直相信的归宿之人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.70,0:14:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定…一定…会背叛他的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.94,0:14:59.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.23,0:15:04.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要救我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:12.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我对负伤的敌人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.62,0:15:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我被那些小三尾解决不是很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.27,0:15:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样不是让人很难承受吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.91,0:15:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:26.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是我 一定会杀掉你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.12,0:15:29.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后无论如何 也要离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.52,0:15:30.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把幽鬼丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.67,0:15:33.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就这么想要得到幽鬼丸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.96,0:15:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.34,0:15:42.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们才是为了得到幽鬼丸的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.37,0:15:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才接近他的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.40,0:15:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要得到三尾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.96,0:15:49.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶的军事力量就更胜人一筹了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.35,0:15:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没必要那么做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.15,0:15:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.11,0:15:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶不是已将九尾及其人柱力纳为己有了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.44,0:16:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有如此强大力量的你们 想对大蛇丸大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.35,0:16:07.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们才没有什么资格指责我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.24,0:16:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是那个人柱力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.98,0:16:20.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不会去使用那股力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.76,0:16:24.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙的力量实在太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.68,0:16:28.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以我的力量根本无法驾驭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.27,0:16:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此不知觉间 总会伤害到同伴们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.36,0:16:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 我绝不会召唤这个家伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:43.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真不该跟他说那些
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.26,0:16:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,思念你的人之所在就是你的归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.81,0:16:55.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 有谁在思念我的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.93,0:16:58.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里就是我的归宿之地咯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.63,0:17:04.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是你说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.66,0:17:07.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 无论怎么被眷念着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:09.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了大蛇丸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.40,0:17:13.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利用幽鬼丸的力量控制三尾的你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:15.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无法饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.09,0:17:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会让幽鬼丸接近尾兽的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:26.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果也变成我这样的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 我不会让那样的事发生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.29,0:17:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不相信你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.64,0:17:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个孩子需要归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:43.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他的母亲过世之时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.17,0:17:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就失去了归宿
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.48,0:17:49.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我要代替他母亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.02,0:17:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为大蛇丸的同党 你有什么资格这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.64,0:17:54.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要告诉幽鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.02,0:17:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的归宿绝不是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.92,0:17:59.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这样也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.77,0:18:05.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 对我而言 那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:10.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幽鬼丸就是我的归宿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.68,0:18:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 现在不是在此闲聊的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你昏迷的这段期间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.57,0:18:24.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在附近调查了一番
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.60,0:18:26.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是这里相当复杂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.44,0:18:28.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没能找到类似出口的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:31.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 分头行动的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.90,0:18:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分头行动
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.74,0:18:36.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就你我二人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.76,0:18:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还要更多点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.14,0:18:39.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一千人以上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.96,0:18:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多重影分身之术
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:19:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们三人的任务就是从木叶手里夺回幽鬼丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.35,0:19:05.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为达目的 你们可以不择手段
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.14,0:19:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好享受这份力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.91,0:19:53.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.16,0:19:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:20:00.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一届 鸣人杯争夺战
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.73,0:20:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纪念为从这莫名其妙的地方逃脱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.86,0:20:06.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而寻找出口的大赛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.21,0:20:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.49,0:20:12.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各就各位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.89,0:20:20.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预备 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.64,0:20:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有这么多帮手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.21,0:20:30.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该很快就能找到出口的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 肯定是我先找到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.80,0:20:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.34,0:20:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何 都要尽快离开并找到幽鬼丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:42.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:43.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红莲姐的下落
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定是和鸣人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.82,0:20:51.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在三尾的腹中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.70,0:22:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按幽鬼丸所说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.09,0:22:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晶遁忍者红莲应该还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.62,0:22:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而鸣人则和红莲一起被三尾吞噬了 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.76,0:22:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听起来似乎是无稽之谈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.93,0:22:50.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 你如何确定红莲平安无事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.06,0:22:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果红莲姐发生意外的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.72,0:22:53.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个水晶就会裂开的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.69,0:22:56.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但还是无法确定鸣人的安危
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.59,0:22:58.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在也只能相信他平安无事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.73,0:23:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去寻找三尾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.18,0:23:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.01,0:23:03.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山茶花的路标
